{"tid":1231293,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"联署制裁港英余孽林鄭！好人一生平安！","createTime":"2019-06-16T12:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T12:29:42.000Z","uid":261095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bb770cc2ddcbdc1960bd192d2c370c50fbd819e8","tid":1231293,"uid":261095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:29:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/rt-hon-sajid-javid-british-citizenship-to-be-revoked-from-carrie-lam-s-林鄭月娥-family?recruiter=968704279&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_campaign=psf_combo_share_message&amp;utm_medium=whatsapp&amp;utm_content=washarecopy_16118043_en-CA%3Av2&amp;recruited_by_id=14add450-8931-11e9-9a10-f1646b1fff46\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Frt-hon-sajid-javid-british-citizenship-to-be-revoked-from-carrie-lam-s-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-family%3Frecruiter%3D968704279%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_campaign%3Dpsf_combo_share_message%26utm_medium%3Dwhatsapp%26utm_content%3Dwasharecopy_16118043_en-CA%253Av2%26recruited_by_id%3D14add450-8931-11e9-9a10-f1646b1fff46&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=ebaf8873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/rt-hon-sajid-javid-british-citizenship-to-be-revoked-from-carrie-lam-s-林鄭月娥-family?recruiter=968704279&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_campaign=psf_combo_share_message&amp;utm_medium=whatsapp&amp;utm_content=washarecopy_16118043_en-CA%3Av2&amp;recruited_by_id=14add450-8931-11e9-9a10-f1646b1fff46</a><br />\n<br />\nBTW今日發夢夢見自己係遊行隊伍入面，有個呀叔係咁loop「打倒林鄭月娥，女魔頭，拉佢返大陸坐監」，係夢中隱約記得佢仲好手舞足蹈，活潑可愛。<br />\n<br />\n然後有另一個遊行緊嘅呀叔頂唔順，係到屌佢係咁播出黎虐待人，叫佢去同政府講，唔好係到擾民。活潑呀叔又話返佢，佢係到遊行都係同政府訴求架啦，之後我就醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}